ab Spring|Arab Spring movement]]\n\n==== Asian ====\n{{main|Populism#Africa and Asia|l1=Populism in Asia}}\n** [[ELAM (Cyprus)|ELAM]]\n** [[Progressive Party of Working People]]\n** [[Solidarity Movement (Cyprus)|Solidarity Movement]]\n* [[Populism#Georgia|Georgia]]\n** [[Alliance of Patriots of Georgia]]\n* [[Populism#India|India]]\n** [[Bahujan Samaj Party]]\n*** [[Ambedkarism]]\n** [[Hindutva]]\n*** [[Bharatiya Janata Party]]\n**** [[Prime Minister Narendra Modi|Modism]]\n* [[Populism#Iran|Iran]]\n** [[Iranian Green Movement]]\n* [[Populism#Pakistan|Pakistan]]\n** [[Tehreek-e-Insaf]]\n* [[Populism#Turkey|Turkey]]\n** [[Justice and Development Party (Turkey)|Justice and Development Party]]\n*** [[Erdo\u011fanism]]\n** [[Kemalism]]\n** [[Nationalist Movement Party]]\n*** [[\u0130yi Party]]\n** [[Peoples' Democratic Party (Turkey)|Peoples' Democratic Party]]\n\n==== American ====\n{{main|Populism#North America|Populism#Latin America|l1=Populism in North America|l2=Populism in Latin America}}\n* [[Populism in Latin America|Latin America]]\n** [[Front for Victory|Argentina]]\n*** [[Kirchnerism]]\n*** [[Peronism]]\n** [[Populism in Latin America#Populist socialism|Bolivia]]\n*** [[Movement for Socialism (Bolivia)|Movement for Socialism]]\n** [[History of the socialist movement in Brazil|Brazil]]\n*** [[Jair Bolsonaro#Political views|Bolsonarism]]\n*** [[Lulism]]\n*** [[Workers' Party (Brazil)|Petism]]\n*** [[Podemos (Brazil)|Podemos]]\n** [[Populism in Latin America#Chile|Chile]]\n*** [[Carlos Ib\u00e1\u00f1ez del Campo|Iba\u00f1ism]]\n** [[Populism in Latin America#Populist socialism|Ecuador]]\n*** [[PAIS Alliance]]\n**** [[Rafael Correa#Political ideology|Correanism]]\n** [[National Regeneration Movement|Mexico]]\n** [[Populism in Latin America#Populist socialism|Nicaragua]]\n*** [[Sandinism]]\n** [[Puerto Rican Independence Party|Puerto Rico]]\n** [[Populism in Latin America#Populist socialism|Venezuela]]\n*** [[Bolivarianism]]\n**** [[Chavism]]\n**** [[Fifth Republ