ty]]\n* [[People's Republic of Zanzibar|Zanzibar]]\n** [[Afro-Shirazi Party]]\n\n==== American ====\n{{American socialism}}\n{{main|History of socialism#Americas|l1=Socialism in America}}\n* [[African-Caribbean leftism|Caribbean]]\n** [[People's Revolutionary Government (Grenada)|Granada]]\n*** [[New Jewel Movement]]\n* [[Socialism of the 21st century|Latin America]]\n** [[Socialist Party (Argentina)|Argentina]]\n*** [[Piquetero]]s\n** [[Movement for Socialism (Bolivia)|Bolivia]]\n*** [[Fejuve]]\n** [[History of the socialist movement in Brazil|Brazil]]\n*** [[Landless Workers' Movement]]\n*** [[Workers' Party (Brazil)|Workers' Party]]\n** [[Socialist Party of Chile|Chile]]\n** [[Patriotic Union (Colombia)|Colombia]]\n** [[Broad Front (Costa Rica)|Costa Rica]]\n** [[PAIS Alliance|Ecuador]]\n** [[Mexican Revolution|Mexico]]\n*** [[Magonism]]\n*** [[Zapatismo|Zapatism]]\n**** [[Neozapatismo|Neo-Zapatism]]\n***** [[Zapatista Army of National Liberation|Zapatistas]]\n** [[New Left#Latin America|New Left]]\n** [[Sandinista National Liberation Front|Nicaragua]]\n*** [[Sandinismo]]\n** [[Guas\u00fa Front|Paraguay]]\n** [[Broad Front (Uruguay)|Uruguay]]\n** [[United Socialist Party of Venezuela|Venezuela]]\n* [[Socialism#North America|North America]]\n** [[Socialism in Canada|Canada]]\n** [[History of the socialist movement in the United States|United States]]\n*** [[African-American leftism]]\n*** [[American Left]]\n**** [[Individualist anarchism in the United States|Libertarian socialism]]\n***** [[Left-wing market anarchism|Free-market socialism]]\n***** [[Laissez-faire socialism]]\n**** [[New Left#United States|New Left]]\n\n==== Asian ====\n{{main|History of socialism#Asia|l1=Socialism in Asia}}\n* [[Democratic Republic of Afghanistan|Afghanistan]]\n** [[People's Democratic Party of Afghanistan]]\n* [[Armenian Soviet Socialist Republic|Armenia]]\n* [[Azerbaijan Soviet Socialist Republic|Azerbajan]]\n* [[Socialism in Bangladesh|Bangladesh]]\n** [[Awami League]]\n* [[Buk