ek Soviet Socialist Republic|Uzbekistan]]\n* [[Socialist-oriented market economy|Vietnam]]\n** [[Trotskyism in Vietnam|Trotskyism]]\n* [[Democratic Republic of Yemen|Yemen]]\n** [[Yemeni Socialist Party|South Yemen]]\n\n==== European ====\n{{main|History of socialism#Europe|l1=Socialism in Europe}}\n* [[People's Socialist Republic of Albania|Albania]]\n* [[Social Democracy and Progress|Andorra]]\n* [[Socialist Republic of Bosnia and Herzegovina|Bosnia and Herzegovina]]\n* [[People's Republic of Bulgaria|Bulgaria]]\n** [[Bulgarian Socialist Party]]\n* [[Byelorussian Soviet Socialist Republic|Byelarus]]\n** [[Belarusian People's Republic]]\n*** [[Lithuanian\u2013Byelorussian Soviet Socialist Republic]]\n* [[Socialist Republic of Croatia|Croatia]]\n* [[Movement for Social Democracy|Cyprus]]\n* [[Czechoslovak Socialist Republic|Czechoslovakia]]\n** [[Czech Socialist Republic|Czechia]]\n*** [[Czech Social Democratic Party]]\n** [[Slovak Socialist Republic|Slovakia]]\n*** [[Direction \u2013 Social Democracy]]\n*** [[Slovak Soviet Republic]]\n* [[Popular socialism|Denmark]]\n** [[Red\u2013Green Alliance (Denmark)|Red\u2013Green Alliance]]\n*** [[Socialist People's Party (Denmark)|Socialist People's Party]]\n* [[Estonian Soviet Socialist Republic|Estonia]]\n** [[Commune of the Working People of Estonia]]\n* [[Finnish Socialist Workers' Republic|Finland]]\n** [[Left Alliance (Finland)|Left Alliance]]\n* [[French Left|France]]\n** [[French Section of the Workers' International]]\n** [[French Workers' Party]]\n** [[G\u00e9n\u00e9ration.s]]\n** [[Left\u2013right political spectrum#History of the terms|Historical Left]]\n** [[Jacobin (politics)#France|Jacobinism]]\n*** [[Jacobins]]\n**** [[Cordeliers]]\n**** [[Dantonists]]\n**** [[H\u00e9bertists]]\n**** [[The Mountain|Montagnards]]\n***** [[The Mountain (1849)|Democratic Socialists]]\n**** [[Sans-culottes]]\n** [[New Left in Europe|New Left]]\n** [[Opportunist Republicans|Republican Left]]\n** [[Socialist Party (France)|Socialist Party]]\n* [[History of the Social Democratic Party of Germany|Germany]]\n** [[East Germany]] \n*** [[Socialist Unity Party of Germany]]\n** [[German Revolution of 1918\u201319#Saturday, 9 November 1918: two proclamations of a republic|Free Socialist Republic of Germany]]\n*** [[People's State of Bavaria]]\n**** [[Bavarian Soviet Republic]]\n*** [[Soviet Republic of Saxony]]\n** [[General German Workers' Association]]\n** [[Independent Social Democratic Party of Germany]]\n** [[The Left (Germany)|The Left]]\n** [[Social Democratic Workers' Party of Germany]]\n*** [[Social Democratic Party of Germany]]\n** [[West Germany]]\n*** [[History of the Social Democratic Party of Germany#History after World War II|Social Democratic Party of Germany]]\n* [[Syriza|Greece]]\n* [[Hungarian People's Republic|Hungary]]\n** [[Hungarian Soviet Republic]]\n** [[Socialist Party of Hungary]]\n* [[Social Democratic Alliance|Iceland]]\n** [[Left-Green Movement|Left\u2013Green Movement]]\n* [[Socialism#Ireland|Ireland]]\n** [[Labour Party (Ireland)|Labour Party]]\n** [[Sinn F\u00e9in]]\n** [[Solidarity\u2013People Before Profit]]\n* [[Italian Socialist Party|Italy]]\n** [[Biennio Rosso]]\n** [[Action Party (Italy, 1848)|Historical Left]]\n*** [[Historical Far Left]]\n**** [[Italian Radical Party]]\n** [[Italian Left]]\n* [[Latvian Soviet Socialist Republic|Latvia]]\n* [[Lithuanian Soviet Socialist Republic|Lithuania]]\n** [[Lithuanian\u2013Byelorussian Soviet Socialist Republic]]\n* [[Socialist Republic of Macedonia|Macedonia]]\n* [[Moldavian Soviet Socialist Republic|Moldova]]\n** [[Party of Socialists of the Republic of Moldova]]\n* [[Socialist Republic of Montenegro|Montenegro]]\n* [[Socialism in the Netherlands|Netherlands]]\n** [[Socialist Party (Netherlands)|Socialist Party]]\n* [[Labour Party (Norway)|Norway]]\n** [[Socialist Left Party (Norway)|Socialist Left Party]]\n* [[Polish People's Republic|Poland]]\n** [[Democratic Left Alliance]]\n* [[Socialist Party (Portugal)|Portugal]