ism|Anarcho-communsim]]\n*** [[Industrial Workers of the World|Anarcho-syndicalism]]\n**** [[Industrial Workers of the World philosophy and tactics|Wobblyism]]\n*** [[Individualist anarchism in the United States#American egoism|Egoist anarchism]]\n**** [[The Right to Be Greedy|Communist egoism]]\n*** [[Free-market anarchism#Individualist anarchism in the United States|Free-market anarchism]]\n*** [[Green anarchism#Mid-20th century|Green anarchism]]\n*** [[Individualist anarchism in the United States|Individualist anarchism]]\n*** [[Laissez-faire socialism|Laissez-faire]]\n*** [[Left-wing market anarchism]]\n*** [[Mutualism (economic theory)#Ideological development|Mutualism]]\n*** [[Mutualism (economic theory)#Mutualism today|Neo-mutualism]]\n\n==== Asian ====\n{{main|Anarchism in Asia}}\n* [[Anarchism in Azerbaijan|Azerbaijan]]\n* [[Anarchism in China|China]]\n* [[Anarchism in India|India]]\n* [[Anarchism in Israel|Israel]]\n* [[Anarchism in Japan|Japan]]\n* [[Anarchism in Korea|Korea]]\n* [[Anarchism in Singapore|Singapore]]\n* [[Rojava|Syria]]\n** [[Rojava Revolution|Revolutionary Rojava]]\n*** [[Democratic confederalism]]\n* [[Anarchism in Turkey|Turkey]]\n* [[Anarchism in Vietnam|Vietnam]]\n\n==== European ====\n{{main|Individualist anarchism in Europe|l1=Anarchism in Europe}}\n* [[Anarchism in France|France]]\n** [[Anarcho-naturism#France|Anarcho-naturism]]\n** [[Individualist anarchism in France|Individualist anarchism]]\n* [[Anarchism in Germany|Germany]]\n** [[Individualist anarchism in Europe#Germany|Individualist anarchism]]\n* [[Anarchism in Greece|Greece]]\n* [[Anarchism in Iceland|Iceland]]\n* [[Anarchism in Ireland|Ireland]]\n** [[Individualist anarchism in Europe#United Kingdom and Ireland|Individualist anarchism]]\n* [[Anarchism in Italy|Italy]]\n** [[Anarcho-naturism#Other countries|Anarcho-naturism]]\n** [[Individualist anarchism in Italy|Individualist anarchism]]\n* [[Anarchism in Monaco|Monaco]]\n* [[Anarchism in Poland|Poland]]\n* [[Anarchism i