an (utopian concept)#Utopian socialist New Man|l1=Utopian Socialist New Man}}\n* [[Agrarian communism]]\n* [[Centrist Marxism]]\n* [[Ecocommunism|Eco-communism]]\n* [[Eurocommunism]]\n* [[Proletarian internationalism|International communism]]\n* [[Democracy in Marxism|Marxist democracy]]\n* [[Nihilist communism]]\n* [[Primitive communism]]\n* [[Pre-Marxist communism]]\n* [[Socialism and LGBT rights|Queer communism]]\n* [[World communism]]\n\n=== Religious variants ===\n{{main|Religious communism}}\n{{see also|Communism and religion}}\n* [[Christian communism]]\n** [[Bruderhof Communities|Bruderhofs]]\n** [[Diggers]]\n** [[Hutterites]]\n** [[Shakers]]\n* [[Islamic communism]]\n* [[Jewish left|Jewish communism]]\n\n=== Regional variants ===\n==== African ====\n{{main|History of Communism#Africa|l1=Communism in Africa}}\n* [[MPLA|Angola]]\n* [[People's Revolutionary Party of Benin|Benin]]\n* [[Congolese Party of Labour|Congo]]\n* [[Egyptian Communist Party|Egypt]]\n* [[Eritrean People's Liberation Front|Eritrea]]\n* [[Workers' Party of Ethiopia|Ethiopia]]\n* [[FRELIMO|Mozambique]]\n* [[Somali Revolutionary Socialist Party|Somalia]]\n* [[South African Communist Party|South Africa]]\n** [[Trotskyism in South Africa|Trotskyism]]\n* [[Afro-Shirazi Party|Tanzania]]\n* [[Tunisian Communist Party|Tunisia]]\n\n==== American ====\n{{main|History of communism#Americas|l1=Communism in America}}\n* [[Communism in Canada|Canada]]\n** [[Communism in Quebec|Quebec]]\n* [[Communist Party of Chile|Chile]]\n* [[Communism in Colombia|Colombia]]\n* [[Communist Party of Cuba|Cuba]]\n* [[New Jewel Movement|Grenada]]\n* [[Communism in Peru|Peru]]\n** [[Shining Path]]\n* [[Communism in the United States|United States]]\n\n==== Asian ====\n{{main|History of communism#Asia|l1=Communism in Asia}}\n* [[People's Democratic Party of Afghanistan|Afghanistan]]\n* [[Communist Party of Armenia (Soviet Union)|Armenia]]\n* [[Communist Party of Azerbaijan|Azerbajan]]\n* [[Communist Cambodia (disambiguatio