ocracy]]\n* [[Theodemocracy]]\n\n=== Regional variants ===\n==== African ====\n{{main|History of democracy#Africa|l1=Democracy in Africa}}\n* [[Democracy in Egypt|Egypt]]\n* [[Democracy in Morocco|Morocco]]\n\n==== Asian ====\n{{main|History of democracy#Asia|l1=Democracy in Asia}}\n{{see also|Democracy in the Middle East}}\n* [[Democracy in Bangladesh|Bangladesh]]\n* [[Democracy in Belarus|Belarus]]\n* [[Democracy in China|China]]\n* [[Democracy in Hong Kong|Hong Kong]]\n* [[Democracy in India|India]]\n* [[Democracy in the Middle East#Iran|Iran]]\n* [[Democracy in the Middle East#Israel|Israel]]\n* [[Democracy in the Middle East#Lebanon|Lebanon]]\n* [[Democracy in Pakistan|Pakistan]]\n* [[Democracy in the Middle East#Palestinian Authority|Palestine]]\n* [[Rojava]]\n* [[Representative democracy in Singapore|Singapore]]\n* [[Democracy in Vietnam|Vietnam]]\n\n==== American ====\n{{main|History of democracy#Americas|l1=Democracy in America}}\n* [[Democracy in Chile|Chile]]\n* [[Rebel Zapatista Autonomous Municipalities|Chiapas]]\n* [[Democracy in the United States|United States]]\n** [[History of direct democracy in the United States|Direct democracy]]\n** [[Jacksonian democracy]]\n** [[Jeffersonian democracy]]\n\n==== European ====\n{{main|History of democracy#Europe|l1=Democracy in Europe}}\n* [[History of democracy#Antiquity|Ancient Greece]]\n** [[Athenian democracy]]\n*** [[Kleroterion|Athenian polis democracy]]\n** [[History of democracy#Sparta|Spartan democracy]]\n* [[History of democracy#Rome|Ancient Rome]]\n** [[Democracy in Rome|Roman democracy]]\n* [[French Left|France]]\n** [[Paris Commune]]\n* [[National Democracy|Poland]]\n* [[Democracy in Russia|Russia]]\n** [[Soviet democracy]]\n* [[Landsgemeinde|Switzerland]]\n* [[Democracy in the United Kingdom|United Kingdom]]\n\n==== Oceanian ====\n{{main|History of democracy#Oceania|l1=Democracy in Oceania}}\n* [[Democracy in Australia|Australia]]\n\n== Environmentalism ==\n{{main|Environmentalism}}\n{{see also|Agrarianism|Agricultural economics|Ecological economics|Environmental economics|Environmental movement|Environmental politics|Green party|History of environmentalism|Outline of green politics}}\n{{further|Criticism of environmentalism}}\n; Political internationals\n* [[Friends of the Earth]] ([[environmentalism]])\n* [[Global Greens]] ([[green politics]])\n* [[World Ecological Parties]] ([[bright green environmentalism]])\n\n=== Bright green environmentalism ===\n{{main|Bright green environmentalism}}\n* [[Car-free movement]]\n* [[Climate movement]]\n* [[Conservation movement]]\n* [[Ecomodernism|Eco-modernism]]\n** [[Ecological modernization]]\n** [[Prometheanism]]\n** [[Technogaianism]]\n* [[Positive environmentalism]]\n\n=== Deep green environmentalism ===\n{{main|Deep ecology}}\n* [[Anti-consumerism]]\n** [[Degrowth|Degrowth movement]]\n* [[Anti-globalization movement]]\n** [[Alter-globalization movement]]\n** [[Global justice movement]]\n* [[Anti-nuclear movement]]\n* [[Bioregionalism]]\n* [[Ecocentrism]]\n* [[Eco-fascism]]\n* [[Green anarchism]]\n** [[Anarcho-naturism]]\n** [[Anarcho-primitivism]]\n** [[Communalism]]\n*** [[Eco-communalism]]\n**** [[Back-to-the-land movement]]\n*** [[Democratic confederalism]]\n*** [[Green municipalism]]\n*** [[Libertarian municipalism]]\n*** [[Social ecology (Bookchin)|Social ecology]]\n** [[Inclusive democracy]]\n* [[Neo-Luddism]]\n* [[Radical environmentalism]]\n** [[Animal rights movement]]\n** [[Deep Green Resistance]]\n** [[Earth liberation movement]]\n\n=== Light green environmentalism ===\n{{main|Sustainable development}}\n* [[Free-market environmentalism]]\n** [[Eco-capitalism]]\n*** [[Sustainable capitalism]]\n** [[Georgism]]\n*** [[Geolibertarianism]]\n** [[Green libertarianism]]\n* [[Green conservatism]]\n** [[Fiscal environmentalism]]\n* [[Green liberalism]]\n\n=== Other ===\n{{main|Green politics}}\n* [[Eco-feminism]]\n* [[Eco-nationalism]]\n** [[Green Zionism]]\n* [[Green left]]\n** [[Green communism|Eco-communism]]\