exism|Belgium]]\n** [[Neo-Nazism#Belgium|Neo-Nazism]]\n* [[Neo-Nazism#Bosnia and Herzegovina|Bosnia and Herzegovina]]\n* [[Bulgarian National Socialist Workers Party|Bulgaria]]\n* [[German occupation of Byelorussia during World War II|Belarus]]\n* [[Ustashe|Croatia]]\n** [[Neo-fascism in Croatia|Neo-fascism]]\n** [[Neo-Nazism in Croatia|Neo-Nazism]]\n* [[Neo-Nazism#Czech Republic|Czechia]]\n* [[German National Socialist Workers' Party (Czechoslovakia)|Czechoslovakia]]\n* [[National Socialist Workers' Party of Denmark|Denmark]]\n** [[National Socialist Movement of Denmark|Neo-Nazism]]\n* [[German occupation of Estonia during World War II|Estonia]]\n** [[History of the Jews in Estonia#The Holocaust|Antisemitism]]\n** [[Neo-Nazism#Estonia|Neo-Nazism]]\n* [[French fascism|France]]\n** [[History of the Jews in France#World War II and the Holocaust|Antisemitism]]\n** [[Vichy France|Nazism]]\n*** [[Neo-Nazism#France|Neo-Nazism]]\n** [[Neo-socialism]]\n** [[R\u00e9volution nationale]]\n* [[Nazism|Germany]]\n** [[Nazi Germany]]\n*** [[Antisemitism in Germany|Antisemitism]]\n*** [[Hitlerism]]\n*** [[Strasserism]]\n** [[Neo-Nazism in Germany|Neo-Nazism]]\n* [[Metaxism|Greece]]\n** [[History of the Jews in Greece#World War II, Resistance and the Holocaust|Antisemitism]]\n** [[Greek National Socialist Party|Nazism]]\n*** [[Neo-Nazism in Greece|Neo-Nazism]]\n**** [[Golden Dawn (political party)|Golden Dawn]]\n** [[Neo-fascism in Greece|Neo-fascism]]\n* [[Arrow Cross Party|Hungary]]\n** [[Antisemitism in Hungary|Antisemitism]]\n** [[Hungarian National Socialist Party|Nazism]]\n*** [[Neo-Nazism#Hungary|Neo-Nazism]]\n* [[Italian Fascism|Italy]]\n** [[National Fascist Party|Classical fascism]]\n*** [[Actual idealism]]\n**** [[Italian racial laws|Antisemitism]]\n*** [[Fasci Italiani di Combattimento|Fasci movement]]\n*** [[Futurist Political Party|Futurism]]\n*** [[Mussolinism]]\n*** [[Republican Fascist Party|Republican fascism]]\n*** [[Revolutionary Fascist Party|Revolutionary fasci