den|Sweden]]\n** [[Antisemitism in Sweden#Fascists, Nazis and the Holocaust|Sweden]]\n** [[Neo-Nazism in Sweden|Neo-Nazism]]\n* [[Neo-Nazism#Switzerland|Switzerland]]\n* [[Reichskommissariat Ukraine|Ukraine]]\n** [[Antisemitism in Ukraine#Antisemitism in Ukraine#World War II|Antisemitism]]\n** [[Neo-Nazism in Ukraine|Neo-Nazism]]\n* [[British fascism|United Kingdom]]\n** [[Neo-fascism in the United Kingdom|Neo-fascism]]\n* [[Yugoslav Radical Union|Yugoslavia]]\n** [[Nazi occupation of Yugoslavia|Antisemitism]]\n\n==== Oceanian ====\n{{main|Fascism#Oceania|l1=Fascism in Oceania}}\n* [[Neo-Nazism#Australia|Australia]]\n* [[Fascism in New Zealand|New Zealand]]\n** [[Neo-Nazism#Oceania|Neo-Nazism]]\n\n== Identity politics ==\n{{main|Identity politics}}\n{{see also|Minority rights}}\n{{further|Identity politics#Debates and criticism|Intersectionality|Politically correct|Politically incorrect|Regressive left|l1=Criticism of identity politics}}\n; Political internationals\n* [[International Council of Women]] ([[feminism]])\n* [[Minority Rights Group International]] ([[minority rights]])\n* [[Unrepresented Nations and Peoples Organization]] ([[indigenous rights]] and [[self-determination]])\n\n=== Age-related rights movements ===\n* [[Children's rights movement]]\n* [[Elder rights|Elder rights movement]]\n* [[Intergenerational equity]]\n* [[Youth rights|Youth rights movement]]\n\n=== Animal-related rights movements ===\n* [[Abolitionism (animal rights)|Abolitionism]]\n* [[Egalitarianism#Egalitarianism and non-human animals|Animal egalitarianism]]\n** [[Anti-specism]]\n* [[Animal protectionism]]\n* [[Animal rights|Animal rights movement]]\n* [[Animal liberation movement]]\n* [[Animal welfare|Animal welfarism]]\n** [[Antinaturalism (politics)|Anti-naturalism]]\n\n=== Disability-related rights movements ===\n* [[Disability rights movement]]\n** [[Deaf culture|Deaf rights movement]]\n** [[Neurodiversity|Neurodiversity movement]]\n*** [[Autism rights movement]]\n*** [[Mad Pride