ism]]\n\n==== Regional variants ====\n{{see also|1989 Tiananmen Square protests|Free school movement|Free Speech Movement|Port Huron Statement}}\n{{further|May 68|Protests of 1968}}\n* [[Student activism#Argentina|Argentina]]\n* [[Student activism#Australia|Australia]]\n* [[Student politics of Bangladesh|Bangladesh]]\n* [[Student activism in canada|Canada]]\n* [[2011\u201313 Chilean student protests|Chile]]\n* [[Student activism#China|China]]\n* [[Student activism#Democratic Republic of Congo|Congo]]\n* [[Student activism#Eastern Europe and the post-Soviet Union states|Eastern Europe]]\n** [[MJAFT!|Albania]]\n** [[Zubr (political organization)|Belarus]]\n** [[Prague Spring|Czechoslovakia]]\n** [[Kmara|Georgia]]\n** [[Hungarian Revolution of 1956|Hungary]]\n** [[KelKel|Kyrgyzstan]]\n** [[Otpor!|Serbia]]\n** [[PORA|Ukraine]]\n* [[European Students' Union|European Union]]\n** [[May 1968 events in France|France]]\n** [[German student movement|Germany]]\n** [[2010 United Kingdom student protests|United Kingdom]]\n* [[Student activism#Hong Kong|Hong Kong]]\n** [[Umbrella Revolution]]\n*** [[2014 Hong Kong class boycott campaign|922/926 Class Boycott]]\n** [[Hong Kong Federation of Students]]\n** [[Moral and National Education controversy#Pressure groups and protests|Occupy Tamar]]\n** [[Scholarism]]\n** [[Umbrella Movement]]\n* [[Student activism#India|India]]\n** [[Assam Movement]]\n** [[2017 pro-jallikattu protests|Pro-jallikattu movement]]\n* [[Student activism#Indonesia|Indonesia]]\n* [[Student activism#Iran|Iran]]\n* [[Student activism#Israel|Israel]]\n* [[Student activism#Japan|Japan]]\n* [[Student movements in Korea|Korea]]\n* [[Student activism#Malaysia|Malaysia]]\n* [[Student activism#M\u00e9xico|Mexico]]\n* [[Student activism#Philippines|Philippines]]\n* [[Student activism#Taiwan|Taiwan]]\n** [[Anti-Black Box Curriculum Movement]]\n** [[Sunflower Student Movement]]\n* [[Student movements in Uganda|Uganda]]\n* [[Student activism#United States|United States]]\n** 