ipartism|Welfare state}}\n{{further|Economic liberalism|Economic globalization|Free trade|Social democracy#Response to neoliberalism (1979\u20131990s)|l4=Social democracy and neo-liberalism}}\n* [[Social corporatism|Social democratic corporatism]]\n* [[Social populism|Social democratic populism]]\n* [[Shachtmanism#Social democratic Shachtmanism|Social democratic Shachtmanism]]\n* [[Democratic transhumanism|Social democratic transhumanism]]\n* [[Welfare state#Three worlds of the welfare state|Social democratic welfarism]]\n* [[Third Way]]\n\n=== Regional variants ===\n==== African ====\n{{main|African socialism|l1=Social democracy in Africa}}\n* [[Nasserism|Egypt]]\n* [[Nkrumaism|Ghana]]\n* [[Guinean People's Assembly|Guinea]]\n* [[Harambee|Kenya]]\n* [[Ujamaa|Tanzania]]\n* [[Socialism in Tunisia|Tunisia]]\n\n==== American ====\n{{main|History of socialism#Americas|l1=Social democracy in America}}\n* [[African-Caribbean leftism|Caribbean]]\n* [[Socialism of the 21st century|Latin America]]\n** [[Socialist Party (Argentina)|Argentina]]\n** [[Movement for Socialism (Bolivia)|Bolivia]]\n** [[History of the socialist movement in Brazil|Brazil]]\n** [[Socialist Party of Chile|Chile]]\n** [[Patriotic Union (Colombia)|Colombia]]\n** [[National Liberation Party (Costa Rica)|Costa Rica]]\n** [[PAIS Alliance|Ecuador]]\n** [[National Regeneration Movement|Mexico]]\n** [[Sandinista National Liberation Front|Nicaragua]]\n** [[Guas\u00fa Front|Paraguay]]\n** [[Puerto Rican Independence Party|Puerto Rico]]\n** [[Broad Front (Uruguay)|Uruguay]]\n** [[For Social Democracy|Venezuela]]\n* [[Socialism#North America|North America]]\n** [[New Democratic Party|Canada]]\n** [[New Deal|United States]]\n\n==== Asian ====\n{{main|History of socialism#Asia|l1=Social democracy in Asia}}\n* [[Awami League|Bangladesh]]\n* [[Socialist ideology of the Kuomintang|China]]\n* [[Socialism in Hong Kong|Hong Kong]]\n* [[Indian National Congress|India]]\n* [[Marhaenism|Indonesia]]\n* [[Socialism in Iran|Ir