iz Soviet Socialist Republic|Kyrgyzstan]]\n* [[Communism in Korea|Korea]]\n** [[Workers' Party of Korea|North Korea]]\n** [[Progressivism in South Korea|South Korea]]\n* [[Kurdistan Workers' Party|Kurdistan]]\n** [[Democratic Party of Iranian Kurdistan|Iranian Kurdistan]]\n** [[Kurdistan Socialist Democratic Party|Iraqi Kurdistan]]\n** [[Kurdish Democratic Progressive Party|Syrian Kurdistan]]\n** [[Freedom and Socialism Party|Turkish Kurdistan]]\n* [[Lao People's Revolutionary Party|Laos]]\n* [[Mongolian People's Republic|Mongolia]]\n* [[Burmese Way to Socialism|Myanmar]]\n* [[Nepali Congress|Nepal]]\n* [[Socialism in Pakistan|Pakistan]]\n* [[Democratic Alliance List|Palestine]]\n* [[Pakistan Peoples Party|Pakistan]]\n* [[Akbayan|Philippines]]\n* [[Ba'athism|Syria]]\n** [[Rojava]]\n*** [[Democratic confederalism]]\n*** [[Rojava Revolution|Revolutionary Rojava]]\n** [[Democratic Union Party (Syria)|Syrian Kurdistan]]\n** [[United Arab Republic]]\n* [[Tajik Soviet Socialist Republic|Tajikistan]]\n* [[Peoples' Democratic Party (Turkey)|Turkey]]\n* [[Turkmen Soviet Socialist Republic|Turkmenistan]]\n* [[Uzbek Soviet Socialist Republic|Uzbekistan]]\n* [[Socialist-oriented market economy|Vietnam]]\n** [[Trotskyism in Vietnam|Trotskyism]]\n* [[Democratic Republic of Yemen|Yemen]]\n** [[Yemeni Socialist Party|South Yemen]]\n\n==== European ====\n{{main|History of socialism#Europe|l1=Socialism in Europe}}\n* [[People's Socialist Republic of Albania|Albania]]\n* [[Social Democracy and Progress|Andorra]]\n* [[Socialist Republic of Bosnia and Herzegovina|Bosnia and Herzegovina]]\n* [[People's Republic of Bulgaria|Bulgaria]]\n** [[Bulgarian Socialist Party]]\n* [[Byelorussian Soviet Socialist Republic|Byelarus]]\n** [[Belarusian People's Republic]]\n*** [[Lithuanian\u2013Byelorussian Soviet Socialist Republic]]\n* [[Socialist Republic of Croatia|Croatia]]\n* [[Movement for Social Democracy|Cyprus]]\n* [[Czechoslovak Socialist Republic|Czechoslovakia]]\n** [[Czech Socialist Repub